(39,3,1,0,'admin','fasdfasdfasdfasf','mysql','fasdfasdfasdf','fasdfasdfasdfsadfsdfsdf','<p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><span class="js_jump_icon h5_image_link"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" src="http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471442.jpeg" width="678" height="577" title="" alt="" style="width: 678px; height: auto !important;"/></span></p><blockquote style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; padding: 10px 10px 10px 20px; outline: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-color: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.4); color: rgb(89, 89, 89); box-sizing: inherit; overflow: auto; text-size-adjust: inherit; line-height: 1.55em; border-radius: 6px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.1);"><p style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.9em; outline: 0px; line-height: normal;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">Redis分布式存储的常见方案有：<br/></span></p><section><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">1.「主从 (Master-Slave) 模式</span><span style="font-size: 14px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">」</span>主从复制，读写分离，数据备份。</span></section><section><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">2.「哨兵 (Sentinel) 模式</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">」</span>一主多从，哨兵监控，自动处理故障，容错和恢复。</span></section><section><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">3.「&nbsp;集群 (Cluster) 模式</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">」</span>多主多从，数据分片，在线扩容。</span></section><section><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><br/></span></section><section><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">Redis集群切片的方式有：</span></section><section><span style="outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">1.「客户端分片」</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">分片逻辑在Redis客户端实现，采用一致性哈希来决定Redis节点。</span></section><section><span style="outline: 0px; color: rgb(85, 84, 84); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">2.「中间件分片」</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">借助中间件实现Redis节点的路由分派，根据路由规则将请求发送到正确的Redis节点上。</span></section><p style="margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84); outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">3.&nbsp;「客户端服务端分片」</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">Redis Cluster模式，客户端采用一致性哈希，服务端提供错误节点的重定向服务。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;"><br/></span></p><section><span style="color: rgb(85, 84, 84);"><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;">本文将详细介绍「Redis分布式存储</span><span style="outline: 0px; font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;">」<span style="letter-spacing: 0.578px;">的3种方案</span></span>和「Redis集群切片<span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">」</span>的3种常见方式。</span></span></section></blockquote><h2 style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);"><span style="margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);"><br/></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;">什<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">么是Redis集群</span></span></h2><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">Redis集群是由多个redis实例组成的集合，将缓存的数据分散到多个redis节点上存储，减轻单个缓存节点的访问压力，达到分流效果，提高了存储容量和吞吐量，提供高可用性和容错恢复能力，实现了水平扩容。</span></p><h2 style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);"><span style="margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);"></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;">R<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">edis<span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;">集群的作用和优势</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span></span></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"></span><span style="margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;"></span></h2><p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 26px; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;">1.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 164, 231);"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.5px;">处理大规模数据</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 0.5px;">：<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">将数据分散在多个节点上，从而突破单节点内存限制，有效应对数据量的增长和高并发的访问请求。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 164, 231);"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px;">高可用性</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">：<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">当主节点发生故障时，集群会自动选举新的主节点，从而实现故障转移，保证高可用性。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 164, 231);"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">可扩展性</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">：Redis集群可以根据业务需求和系统负载，动态添加或删除节点，实现水平扩展，以适应数据规模的变化。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">4.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 164, 231);"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">高性能</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：Redis集群中的各个节点可以并行处理不同的请求，从而提高系统整体吞吐量和响应速度，适合于高并发访问的场景。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">5.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 164, 231);"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">自动故障转移</span></strong></span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：Redis集群通过哨兵节点监控主节点的健康状态，在主节点故障时，自动选举新的主节点，减少服务中断和数据丢失的风险。</span></p><h2 style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);"><span style="margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);"><br/></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">1&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">主</span><span style="letter-spacing: normal;">从（Master - Slave）模式</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span></span></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"></span><span style="margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「主从模式的原理」</span></strong></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">主从模式是指在Redis集群中有</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">一个主节点(Master)和多个从节点(Slave)。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">Master节点负责数据的写操作，Slave节点负责数据的读操作。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">通过主从复制，将Master节点的数据变更同步到Slave节点。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「主从模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">1.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">数据备份</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：通过主从复制，从节点备份主节点的数据，提高数据可靠性。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">2.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">读写分离</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：将读操作和写操作分配给不同的节点处理，提高系统稳定性。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">3.&nbsp;</span><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">提升读取性能</span></strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提高数据的查询效率。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「主从模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">1.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">没有容错和恢复的能力</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">，</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">存在单点故障</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">：一旦Master节点故障，不会自动选出新的主节点，导致后续所有的写操作直接失败。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">2.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">可用性低</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">：主节点故障时不能自动实现故障转移，需要人工干预手动切换，故障恢复时间长。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">没有实现数据分片</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">，</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">无法在线扩容</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。<br/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">4.&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">5.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">单个主节点承担所有写操作</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「主从模式的应用场景」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">适用于数据备份、读写分离、对可用性要求不高，小规模数据处理的场景。</span></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap; text-align: center;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" src="http://www.tp6.com/download_img/20231028/WeChat_1698471443.png" width="678" height="367" title="" alt="" style="width: 678px; height: auto !important;"/></p><p style="text-wrap: wrap;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"></span></p><h2 style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);"><span style="margin-bottom: -22px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8EXvgrCpDyhrAoOko6Mwicgpp3TuwW3YoPJpJqfEqryDG3IIdcbdx9LJhCOqDXCq9u1J1uSSVgVHQ/640?wx_fmt=png&quot;);"><br/></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">2&nbsp;</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"><span style="letter-spacing: 2px;">哨</span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;">兵（Sentinel）模式</span></span><span style="letter-spacing: normal;"></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span></span></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"></span><span style="margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的原理」</span></strong><br/></section><section><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;">哨兵模式是在Redis主从集群的基础上加入了哨兵节点，监控主节点和从节点的状态。当Master节点出现故障时，哨兵节点会</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">自动从剩余的Slave节点中选举出一个新的Master节点</span></strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;">，并通知其他Slave节点和客户端。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">1.</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">&nbsp;高可用性</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：提供故障的自动处理能力。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">2.</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">&nbsp;容灾恢复</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：在主从模式数据备份的基础上，提供容错和自动恢复机制。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);"><strong>读写分离</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提升读取性能。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">4.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);"><strong>解决了单点故障</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：监测到master节点故障，会自动从slave节点中选出一个节点将其切换成master节点，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">在选举结束之前，redis会开启保护机制，禁止写操作</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">，直到新的master节点产生。每个哨兵节点都是一个独立的进程，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">哨兵节点之间也会互相监控</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">1. 依然没有实现数据分片，无法在线扩容，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">2. 每个从节点和主节点的耦合度高，在主节点宕机到重新选举Master的期间，服务不可用。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, 