pan style="letter-spacing: normal;"></span></span><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"></span></span></span><span style="margin-left: 25px; outline: 0px; display: flex; color: rgb(64, 184, 250); font-size: 20px;"></span><span style="margin-top: -10px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 200px; height: 10px; border-top-left-radius: 20px; background: rgba(64, 184, 250, 0.5); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; justify-content: flex-end; float: right;"><br/></span></h2><p><br/></p><section><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的原理」</span></strong><br/></section><section><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;">哨兵模式是在Redis主从集群的基础上加入了哨兵节点，监控主节点和从节点的状态。当Master节点出现故障时，哨兵节点会</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">自动从剩余的Slave节点中选举出一个新的Master节点</span></strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); letter-spacing: 1px;">，并通知其他Slave节点和客户端。</span></section><p><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的优点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">1.</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">&nbsp;高可用性</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：提供故障的自动处理能力。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">2.</span><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);">&nbsp;容灾恢复</span></strong><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：在主从模式数据备份的基础上，提供容错和自动恢复机制。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">3.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);"><strong>读写分离</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：通过多个从节点来分担读操作的压力，提升读取性能。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">4.&nbsp;</span><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px; color: rgb(0, 159, 78);"><strong>解决了单点故障</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">：监测到master节点故障，会自动从slave节点中选出一个节点将其切换成master节点，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">在选举结束之前，redis会开启保护机制，禁止写操作</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">，直到新的master节点产生。每个哨兵节点都是一个独立的进程，</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">哨兵节点之间也会互相监控</span><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(1, 171, 255);">「哨兵模式的缺点」</span></strong></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">1. 依然没有实现数据分片，无法在线扩容，并发压力受限于单节点服务器的资源配置。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 1px;">2. 每个从节点和主节点的耦合度高，在主节点宕机到重新选举Master的期间，服务不可用。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">3. 集群中所有节点保存的都是全量数据，浪费内存空间，且数据量过大时严重影响主从同步的速度。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;">4.&nbsp;单个主节点承担所有写操作，写操作受单节点性能瓶颈影响。</span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 0px; text-wrap: wrap; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; outline: 0px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1.6em;"><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; letter-spacing: 2px;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: system-ui, -apple-sy