ystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">。</span></section><section><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; word-spacing: 2px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></section><section><span style="font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.578px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">主从模式和哨兵模式每个节点存储的都是全量的数据，当存储的数据量过大时，就需要对数据进行分片后存储到多个redis实例上。此时就要用到Redis Sharding技术。</span></section><section><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif;">如果数据量很大，那么建议就用cluster。数据量不是很大时，使用sentinel就够了。</span></section><p><br/></p><h2 style="text-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 22px; letter-spacing: 0.578px; outline: 0px; font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, Cambria, Cochin, Georgia, Times, &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-bottom: 4px solid rgb(64, 184, 250);"><span style="margin-bottom: -22px; letter-spacing: 2px; outline: 0px; display: flex; width: 20px; height: 20px; background-size: 20px 20px; background-image: url(&quot;https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ZfyQPSha5X8