td></tr><tr><td data-line-number="14" style="padding: 0px 14px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;user-select: none;text-align: center;vertical-align: top;color: rgb(191, 191, 191);white-space-collapse: collapse;"><br  /></td><td data-line-number="14" style="padding: initial;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;">hwclock --systohc --localtime</td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre><p style="margin: 10px auto;color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;text-wrap: wrap;"><img data-imgfileid="100109267" data-ratio="0.38082191780821917" src="/download_img/20240528/WeChat_1716895258.png" data-type="png" data-w="365" style="border-width: 0px;border-style: initial;border-color: initial;max-width: 740px;cursor: zoom-in;transition: transform 300ms cubic-bezier(0.2, 0, 0.2, 1) 0s !important;"  /></p><h4 style="margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;text-wrap: wrap;">7.3、网络时间同步</h4><pre data-dark-theme="true" highlighted="true" style="margin: 10px auto;transition-duration: 0.2s;transition-property: background, font-size, border-color, border-radius, border-width, padding, margin, color;overflow: auto;font-family: var(--code-font, &#39;&quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif, Consolas, Monaco&#39;);color: rgb(0, 0, 0);font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: left;"><code data-dark-theme="true" style="padding: 1em;font-family: var(--code-font, &#39;&quot;Courier New&quot;, sans-serif, Consolas, Monaco&#39;);transition-duration: 0.2s;transition-property: background, font-size, border-color, border-radius, border-width, padding, margin, color;background: rgb(43, 43, 43);color: rgb(248, 248, 242);display: block;overflow-x: auto;line-height: 1.5;"><table><tbody><tr><td data-line-number="1" style="padding: 0px 14px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;user-select: none;text-align: center;vertical-align: top;color: rgb(191, 191, 191);white-space-collapse: collapse;"><br  /></td><td data-line-number="1" style="padding: initial;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;">安装工具</td></tr><tr><td data-line-number="2" style="padding: 0px 14px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;user-select: none;text-align: center;vertical-align: top;color: rgb(191, 191, 191);white-space-collapse: collapse;"><br  /></td><td data-line-number="2" style="padding: initial;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;">yum -y install ntp ntpdate</td></tr><tr><td data-line-number="3" style="padding: 0px 14px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;user-select: none;text-align: center;vertical-align: top;color: rgb(191, 191, 191);white-space-collapse: collapse;"><br  /></td><td data-line-number="3" style="padding: initial;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;">同步网络时间</td></tr><tr><td data-line-number="4" style="padding: 0px 14px;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initial;border-collapse: initial;min-width: initial;user-select: none;text-align: center;vertical-align: top;color: rgb(191, 191, 191);white-space-collapse: collapse;"><br  /></td><td data-line-number="4" style="padding: initial;border-width: initial;border-style: none;border-color: initi